    "ten": "",
    "hor": "",
    "com": "",
    "ris": "",
    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "cdebe11a-3c4e-4b62-ab0b-2aa38c94e9ea",
    "sentence": "So I think it's hard to know that.",
    "source": "FOMCpresconf20240501.json",
    "doc_type": "press_conference_qa",
    "date": "20240501",
    "context_question": "Nick Timiraos of the Wall Street Journal. Chair Powell, to what extent has the easing in financial conditions since November contributed to the reacceleration in growth, and do you now expect a period of sustained tighter financial conditions will be needed to resume the sort of disinflation the economy saw last year?",
