  {
    "id": "32b34b87-2c0f-4540-8dff-1c7554fd36aa",
    "sentence": "I'm saying we would -- we'd be comfortable cutting rates when we're comfortable cutting rates, and that won't be this year, I don't think.",
    "source": "FOMCpresconf20230726.json",
    "doc_type": "press_conference_qa",
    "date": "20230726",
    "context_question": "So if it’s sort of—sort of stubbornly in maybe the high 2s, you wouldn’t necessarily cut rates?",
