  {
    "id": "dd0ff414-8f4d-45f2-a9aa-7f6223b9f948",
    "sentence": "You know, obviously, what we'll do is we'll look at the totality of the data, as I've mentioned a couple times, and, certainly, the labor data would be important in that.",
    "source": "FOMCpresconf20231213.json",
    "doc_type": "press_conference_qa",
    "date": "20231213",
    "context_question": "But, but would you take that as a signal that you should cut rates?",
    "top": "",
